  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of my friends who were a little older and managed to get into places like Julia Richmond school in New York.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were eased a lot of higher education because the teachers there knew their way around, but my provincial teachers had no idea and were of absolutely no help.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, one of the German teachers that I had-- no, actually she was an English teacher-- insisted that I had an accent and a lisp, and forced me to go into elocution classes, which at our high school were broadcasting.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We broadcast in front of a microphone and read things on the microphone, did funny plays in front of the microphone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she did me an enormous favor by banishing me to that, because my dict-on together with the New York telephone company-- my diction and my expression was a lot of things have stood me in very good stead that it was very helpful as I went along my way.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in the meantime, we were living with my maternal grandparents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My grandfather was diabetic and not well at all, and while we were living together, he had a major stroke, and was paralyzed, and was not able to give himself the insulin injections anymore.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So here my desire in the medical area sort of came through because I was elected to do the insulin injections with him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My grandmother wasn't able to do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She couldn't bring herself to doing it in there twice a day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was his assistant in giving him these injections.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Also, at the same time, my brother was diagnosed with grand mal and had seizures, bad seizures, at unpredictable times.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
